Look around.

1061
01:13:08,474 --> 01:13:12,911
Can't believe you were tipped, huh?
Well, if l had a certain lady here--

1062
01:13:12,978 --> 01:13:15,208
- Where's the jerk? Where's George?
- Right here!

1063
