- My wife and l are going to Boston.

1126
01:20:12,064 --> 01:20:15,227
Our luggage has been checked through,
and l wanna take this bag in the cabin.

1127
01:20:15,300 --> 01:20:17,928
lt exceeds the maximum cabin size
for flight requirements.

1128
01:20:18,003 --> 01:20:21,063
lt does look quite a bit too large
for the passenger compartment.

1129
01:20:21,139 --> 01:20:24,836
Sir, those are our flight regulations,
designed for your comfort and safety.

1130
01:20:24,910 --> 01:20:27,708
- l can't make the trip without it.
- You really can't?

1131
01:20:27,779 --> 01:20:31,545
- Absolutely not.
- ln that case, l think we can--

1132
01:20:31,616 --> 01:20:33,709
l know it's past
cancellation time...

1133
01:20:33,785 --> 01:20:36,845
but under the circumstances
l think we might stretch a point.

1134
01:20:36,922 --> 01:20:39,049
We'll give you full rebate
on your tickets.

1135
01:20:39,124 --> 01:20:41,649
Wait a minute.
l don't want a rebate.

1136
01:20:41,727 --> 01:20:44,321
Well, sir, l don't know
what else to suggest.

1137
01:20:44,396 --> 01:20:46,921
lt's close to flight time.
There are other passengers waiting.

1138
01:20:46,999 --> 01:20:49,194
Perhaps the gentleman's
worried about the contents.

1139
01:20:49,267 --> 01:20:51,758
- We'd be happy to insure it.
- We'd be delighted.

1140
01:20:51,837 --> 01:20:54,271
lf you'd give me its estimated value
and tell me what's in it.

1141
01:20:54,339 --> 01:20:59,299
There's nothing in it.
Just personal items, things like that.

1142
01:20:59,378 --> 01:21:01,938
All right, check it through.

1143
01:21:02,014 --> 01:21:05,506
Thank you, sir. You'll find the service
to your complete satisfaction.

1144
01:21:05,584 --> 01:21:07,950
...flight 40,
the New Englander...

1145
01:21:08,020 --> 01:21:12,013
DC-7 service to Boston
at gate eight.

1146
01:21:38,750 --> 01:21:41,241
No, Sebastian.

1147
01:21:41,319 --> 01:21:43,685
Was we frightened
by the airplane?

1148
01:21:43,755 --> 01:21:47,054
We go for trip
on nice airplane someday.

1149
01:22:05,844 --> 01:22:07,004
Come back here!

1150
01:22:51,256 --> 01:22:53,349
Mr. Preston,
we'll be announcing boarding--

1151
01:22:56,128 --> 01:22:59,495
Grimes speaking. What?

1152
01:22:59,564 --> 01:23:02,397
Oh, you're not serious?

1153
01:23:02,467 --> 01:23:04,799
Right out on the runway?

1154
01:23:04,870 --> 01:23:06,804
Yes, sir.
Right away.

1155
01:23:13,011 --> 01:23:14,945
Will passenger Preston...

1156
01:23:15,013 --> 01:23:18,380
please report to
the American Airlines ticket counter.

1157
01:23:25,690 --> 01:23:26,384
Taxi!

1158
01:23:49,214 --> 01:23:51,546
Johnny, you've got to run.

1159
01:23:51,616 --> 01:23:54,983
Nah. What's the difference?


